unittitle_ssm: Philip Howard photographs of the Racquet and Tennis Club
abstract_ssm: A portfolio of twenty-seven 16 x 20-inch archivally printed photographs by Philip Howard of the exterior and interiors of the Racquet and Tennis Club at 370 Park Avenue, a McKim, Mead & White-designed building completed in 1918. Also includes a book containing the same photographs and 14 additional views.
